---
title: Frequently Asked Questions
description: Got questions about Land Shark Tours in Santa Barbara? Find answers about tour length, tickets, accessibility, parking, weather cancellations, and more.
keywords: Land Shark Tours FAQ, Santa Barbara amphibious tour questions, Land Shark Tours tickets, Santa Barbara tour accessibility, public tour questions Santa Barbara
---

{% extends "layouts/base.njk" %}

{% block content %}

  {% include "components/page-hero.njk" %}

  <section class="py-12 lg:py-16">
    <div class="max-w-screen-xl mx-auto px-4 lg:px-6">
      <p class="text-teal font-semibold text-lg mb-10">For Public Tours</p>

      <div class="max-w-3xl divide-y divide-gray-100">

        <div class="py-6">
          <h2 class="font-heading text-xl text-navy mb-2">How long is the tour?</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Approximately 90 minutes, half on land, half at sea.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="py-6">
          <h2 class="font-heading text-xl text-navy mb-2">Do we have to stop and wait for people to get on and off during the tour?</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600">No, tours are nonstop fun!</p>
        </div>

        <div class="py-6">
          <h2 class="font-heading text-xl text-navy mb-2">Is there a guide on board?</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Yes, every public tour is narrated with an amazing award winning tour guide.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="py-6">
          <h2 class="font-heading text-xl text-navy mb-2">Are there restrooms on board?</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600">No, restrooms are available at the departure and return location before and after every tour.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="py-6">
          <h2 class="font-heading text-xl text-navy mb-2">Are babies free?</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Yes, there is no charge for children under the age of 2 if they are seated in your lap.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="py-6">
          <h2 class="font-heading text-xl text-navy mb-2">Is there stroller or wheelchair storage?</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Yes, the crew may bring it on board or lock and store it at the departure location.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="py-6">
          <h2 class="font-heading text-xl text-navy mb-2">Where do I get tickets?</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Tickets can be purchased online or there are a limited number of non-advance seats available for purchase as you board — first come, first serve. Cash and credit cards are accepted.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="py-6">
          <h2 class="font-heading text-xl text-navy mb-2">Can I make a reservation?</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Yes, tour tickets can be purchased online. Advance ticket inquiries can be made via email to <a href="mailto:LandAndSeaTours@aol.com" class="text-teal font-semibold hover:underline">LandAndSeaTours@aol.com</a>.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="py-6">
          <h2 class="font-heading text-xl text-navy mb-2">Can we bring food or drinks?</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Food and alcoholic beverages are not permitted on public tours.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="py-6">
          <h2 class="font-heading text-xl text-navy mb-2">How early should I arrive?</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600">At least 15 minutes prior to departure. Allow more time for large groups and during holidays.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="py-6">
          <h2 class="font-heading text-xl text-navy mb-2">What should I wear?</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Bring a jacket or sweatshirt — it may be cooler while at sea.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="py-6">
          <h2 class="font-heading text-xl text-navy mb-2">Do the tours run in bad weather?</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600">The captain may cancel tours at any time if hazardous conditions are present.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="py-6">
          <h2 class="font-heading text-xl text-navy mb-2">Is it easy to get on board?</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Yes, there are seven steps with handrails on either side. Crewmembers are able to assist all passengers during boarding and disembarking.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="py-6">
          <h2 class="font-heading text-xl text-navy mb-2">Will I get seasick?</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600">No.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="py-6">
          <h2 class="font-heading text-xl text-navy mb-2">How many seats are available on each tour?</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600">40 people.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="py-6">
          <h2 class="font-heading text-xl text-navy mb-2">Is there parking nearby?</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Yes, street parking on Cabrillo Blvd and Chapala St., and on Stearns Wharf.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="py-6">
          <h2 class="font-heading text-xl text-navy mb-2">Are there discounts?</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Discounts are not available.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="py-6">
          <h2 class="font-heading text-xl text-navy mb-2">Can I book a private tour?</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Yes, please see our <a href="{{ "/charter/" | url }}" class="text-teal font-semibold hover:underline">private charter page</a> for more information.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="py-6">
          <h2 class="font-heading text-xl text-navy mb-2">Are gift certificates available?</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Yes, gift certificates can be purchased over the phone or on board. You can also <a href="{{ "/gift-cards/" | url }}" class="text-teal font-semibold hover:underline">purchase gift cards online</a>.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="py-6">
          <h2 class="font-heading text-xl text-navy mb-2">Can we feed the sharks?</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Yes, only on land at the end of the tour.</p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

{% endblock %}
